<div class="flex flex-row justify-center">
<form id="survey" class="flex flex-col shadow-2xl max-w-screen-md border-solid rounded-xl p-4">

<div class="w-auto flex flex-col items-start">
    <div id="location" class="p-3">
        <p class="mb-2">Where are you located?</p>
            <button class="ml-5 bg-white py-2 px-3 border border-gray-300 rounded-md shadow-sm text-sm leading-4 font-medium text-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-50 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-offset-2 focus:ring-blue-500" id="find-me">Find My Location</button>
            <p id="location-name"></p>
        </input> 
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>How do you identify?</p>
            <select class="dropdown" id="gender" name="gender">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="man">Man</option>
                <option value="woman">Woman</option>
                <option value="other">Other</option>
            </select>
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>Please choose who you would prefer to hike with</p>
            <select class="dropdown"  id="gender-preference" name="gender-preference">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="men">Men</option>
                <option value="women">Women</option>
                <option value="no-preference">No Preference</option>
            </select>
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>How far do you like to hike?</p>
            <select class="dropdown" id="hike-distance" name="hike-distance">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="easy">1-2 miles. Nothing crazy.</option>
                <option value="medium">Under 5 miles. Solid stroll.</option>
                <option value="hard">5-10 miles. Light work</option>
                <option value="very-hard">10+ miles. Getting after it.</option>
            </select>
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>At what pace do you prefer to hike?</p>
            <select class="dropdown"  id="hike-pace" name="hike-pace">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="slow">Slow</option>
                <option value="moderate">Moderate</option>
                <option value="fast">Fast</option>
            </select>
    </div>

    <div class="p-3">
        <p>Do you hike with a pet? (Emotional support peacocks not applicable)</p>
            <select class="dropdown" id="with-pet" name="with-pet">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="true">Yes</option>
                <option value="false">No</option>
            </select>
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>What is your favorite hiking climate?</p>
            <select class="dropdown" id="hike-climate" name="hike-climate">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="desert">Desert</option>
                <option value="snow">Snow</option>
                <option value="rainy">Rainy</option>
                <option value="arid">Arid</option>

            </select>
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>Will you hike in snow?</p>
            <select class="dropdown" id="hike-snow" name="hike-snow">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="true">Yes</option>
                <option value="false">No</option>
            </select>
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>Do you like hiking to a water feature</p>
            <select class="dropdown" id="water-feature" name="water-feature">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="true">Yes</option>
                <option value="false">No</option>
            </select>
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>Do you enjoy bagging peaks? AKA hiking to the summit?</p>
            <select  class="dropdown"id="peaks" name="peaks">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="true">Yes</option>
                <option value="false">No</option>
            </select>
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>Do you hike with any special equipment?</p>
            <select class="dropdown" id="special-equipment" name="special-equipment">
                <option disable hidden selected>Please choose one</option>
                <option value="true">Yes</option>
                <option value="false">No</option>
            </select>
    </div>
    <div class="p-3">
        <p>Please write a little snippet about yourself and why you love to hike.</p>
        <input type="text" placeholder="Text" id="biography" name="biography" class="mt-1 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:border-blue-500 block w-full shadow-sm sm:text-sm border-gray-300 rounded-md leading-6">
    </div>
   
</div>
